					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><p class="mw-empty-elt"> 
</p>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about the issue of politics in the religion of Islam. For the movement of "Political Islam", see <a href="/wiki/Political_Islam" title="Political Islam">Political Islam</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
